data.description:
Centrally located in one of Dash Points Premiere Areas, this Watchtower estate offers exquisite craftsmanship, meticulous design and state-of-the-art technology. Designed to enjoy the Pacific Northwest surroundings with extraordinary views of the Puget Sound and Cascade Mountain Range, this residence is the perfect combination of elegant spaciousness and warmth. The
Epicurean Kitchen with granite counters, stainless Sub Zero and Viking appliances, opens up to the Great Room with vaulted ceilings and floor to ceiling windows which highlight the magnificent views.  Glass doors lead to an expansive wrap around deck perfect for entertaining. Fabulous floor plan that boasts 5 bedrooms and 5 baths--- perfect for visiting guests. Serene
Master suite with Jacuzzi soaking tub, large two person shower and massive walk-in closet. An ideal melding of elegance and recreation!
data.whatILove: Extraordinary views of the Puget Sound, Mt Rainier, Vashon Island and Cascade Range.   Great living room completed with marble and wood flooring inlay, tons of natural lighting and vaulted ceilings complete the room.  Impressively remolded Kitchen with stainless steel viking and subzero appliances, granite counter-tops and ceramic flooring.   Elegantly remodeled bathrooms with granite counter-tops and ceramic or marble flooring.  The Master suite is exactly that.  All the amenities that a couple could imagine.  Gas Fireplace, jacuzzi soaking tub, walk-in closet with organizer to store all of your needs.  Spacious walk-in two person shower and powder room.  All bedrooms come furnished with walk-in closets and 8 foot entry doors.  An abundant amount of storage and closet space throughout the home for a large families needs.  1800+ sq feet of covered deck for outdoor entertainment with a wet bar. ~1000 square feet of Gym/Recreation room to setup your own personal gym or private training studio.  12 foot ceilings in a massive, 1200sqft, 3 Car Garage with an attached Hobby/man cave/wine room.  All new doors, flooring and cabinets throughout the home.  Central vacuum makes cleaning this massive home a snap.  Climate control on all floors to maximize energy efficiency while maintaining comfort throughout the home.  This house is absolutely beautiful.
